Main RPC inventory
==================

COMMAND_RPC_ACCESS_ACCOUNT
--------------------------
http endpoints: none
json_rpc methods: rpc_access_account
request fields (inherits rpc_request_base): client: std::string, delta_balance: int64_t
response fields (inherits rpc_response_base): credits: uint64_t

COMMAND_RPC_ACCESS_DATA
-----------------------
http endpoints: none
json_rpc methods: rpc_access_data
request fields (inherits rpc_request_base): none
response fields (inherits rpc_response_base): entries: std::list<entry>, hashrate: uint32_t
nested types:
  - entry: client: std::string, balance: uint64_t, last_update_time: uint64_t, credits_total: uint64_t, credits_used: uint64_t, nonces_good: uint64_t, nonces_stale: uint64_t, nonces_bad: uint64_t, nonces_dupe: uint64_t

COMMAND_RPC_ACCESS_INFO
-----------------------
http endpoints: none
json_rpc methods: rpc_access_info
request fields (inherits rpc_access_request_base): none
response fields (inherits rpc_access_response_base): hashing_blob: std::string, seed_height: uint64_t, seed_hash: std::string, next_seed_hash: std::string, cookie: uint32_t, diff: uint64_t, credits_per_hash_found: uint64_t, height: uint64_t

COMMAND_RPC_ACCESS_PAY
----------------------
http endpoints: none
json_rpc methods: rpc_access_pay
request fields (inherits rpc_access_request_base): paying_for: std::string, payment: uint64_t
response fields (inherits rpc_access_response_base): none

