-----------------------
http endpoints: none
json_rpc methods: add_aux_pow
request fields (inherits rpc_request_base): blocktemplate_blob: blobdata, aux_pow: std::vector<aux_pow_t>
response fields (inherits rpc_response_base): blocktemplate_blob: blobdata, blockhashing_blob: blobdata, merkle_root: std::string, merkle_tree_depth: uint32_t, aux_pow: std::vector<aux_pow_t>
nested types:
  - aux_pow_t: id: std::string, hash: std::string

