COMMAND_RPC_SYNC_INFO
---------------------
http endpoints: none
json_rpc methods: sync_info
request fields (inherits rpc_access_request_base): none
response fields (inherits rpc_access_response_base): height: uint64_t, target_height: uint64_t, next_needed_pruning_seed: uint32_t, peers: std::list<peer>, spans: std::list<span>, overview: std::string
nested types:
  - peer: info: connection_info
  - span: start_block_height: uint64_t, nblocks: uint64_t, connection_id: std::string, rate: uint32_t, speed: uint32_t, size: uint64_t, remote_address: std::string

